{"tid":2143332,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紅魔超新星加盟里爾　外借轉戰葡超踢住先","createTime":"2020-08-07T04:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T08:02:25.000Z","uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ccb3e9988730b903b05e33b659563f82b6a436","tid":2143332,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"曼聯「千禧BB」安祖高美斯，上月同紅魔完約後離隊，近日獲法甲球隊里爾青睞加盟球隊，並將直接租借去葡超博維斯塔。<br />\n<br />\n現年19歲嘅安祖高美斯出身於曼聯青訓，2017年5月首次代表紅魔一隊出戰，以16歲263日成為球隊最年輕上陣球員，被視為新世代紅魔小將中，極具天賦嘅新星。<br />\n<br />\n近年唔少英格蘭小將因為喺國內得唔到上陣機會，繼而選擇外闖他國，查頓辛祖就係典型例子，曾被譽為天才小將嘅安祖高美斯，日後亦有望將步查頓辛祖後塵。"},{"pid":"f8aa80bc0328f0c29ac75ef9a21377a4f49c4dcf","tid":2143332,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"曼聯超新星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6e25d32f5ba248fe27f21230ce3ffe801102f4","tid":2143332,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:49:29.000Z","msg":"步查頓辛祖後塵<br />\n唔係負面架咩"},{"pid":"83ff6a9f3694abcb07243f5e788bfd111e67ccbc","tid":2143332,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"仲矮過梅西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705389c6d16aa473340c54116ec5861fe54da517","tid":2143332,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:55:50.000Z","msg":"走左都係外借，咁走嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069f46981c3d46cdba816a3304ed58cd2b2016ca","tid":2143332,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"打機幾勁"},{"pid":"73ecb5a1fc87321213b13a616a8e0d2d128d6290","tid":2143332,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705389c6d16aa473340c54116ec5861fe54da517","tid":2143332,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:55:50.000Z","msg":"走左都係外借，咁走嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/fa